          </summary>
          <div class="p-5 pt-0 text-[var(--text-secondary)] border-t border-[var(--border-color)] mt-2">
            Generally, it is not recommended to soak wood chips. Soaking creates steam rather than clean, thin blue smoke. This steam can lower your smoker's temperature and produce a bitter flavor profile on your meat.
          </div>
        </details>
